                },
                "p": [
                    {
                        "value": "At the time of accessioning, materials were placed in archival housing and a collection-level finding aid was created to describe these materials. Papers and memorabilia were originally loose in a box, and were grouped by the archivist into topical groups and arranged alphabetically."
                    }
